LinkedListTests

Class LinkedListTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • MainClasses.AbstractTest
      • LinkedListTests.LinkedListTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedListAddtest, LinkedListContainsTest, LinkedListGetTest, LinkedListIndexOfTest, LinkedListRemoveTest, LinkedListSizeTest

    public abstract class LinkedListTest
extends AbstractTest
    This is an abstract superclass for all the tests that use the LinkedList data structure. This class handles the initialization of the data structure and adding new instances to the structure. The LinkedList contains instances that are integers. They start from 1 and increase by one with each new instance in the structure.

    Unto Created 1.4.2013.
